{"tid":1334952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我在暹粒的所見所聞","createTime":"2019-07-20T10:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T01:18:36.000Z","uid":284309,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"110af8103528f71a04c384110ed369bbe9c165c6","tid":1334952,"uid":284309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"純粹好想分享比大家聽<br />\n話說小弟自己一個去暹粒<br />\n自己影唔到相就於是搵人幫手影<br />\n咁順手人地/自己都會問番句Where are you from?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>情景一</ins><br />\n有個來自美國既叔叔一聽到我話from Hong Kong<br />\n就開始講起自己有留意近日既新聞<br />\n仲話自己有個長居於香港既葡萄牙朋友<br />\n本身番咗葡萄牙探親都特登買番張機票番香港遊行<br />\n之後就再講吓香港人點團結<br />\n<br />\n<ins>情景二</ins><br />\n有對來自新加坡既情侶一知道我come from Hong Kong<br />\n佢地就問我點睇Carrie Lam<br />\n咁我都有講哂正反兩面既睇法<br />\n佢地都話有香港既朋友而且有一直留意<br />\n然後佢地覺得香港人要勇武可能會失民心但真係無可奈何<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講咁耐都係想表達(可能)其實世界上好多人都留意住甚至係支持我地<br />\n而佢地都不約而同地叫<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span><br />\n雖然小弟人不在香港但心在香港<br />\n(要屌都屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n機票一早買咗而自己都真係想去咗吳哥窟好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>721加油，香港加油。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c2b220095996b811f1b675b4596952c605b94d51","tid":1334952,"uid":284309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:12:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f8cc375fb1a5df53a03e74419b95f5a3c391be2","tid":1334952,"uid":284309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:12:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d9391719a543af27189c786a28469f8352ef7a5","tid":1334952,"uid":284309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f021994848234121f38bc08700864fcc2c70e763","tid":1334952,"uid":284309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:14:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7158711dd11e5981c7dcda52d195a58b60fcecd8","tid":1334952,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:14:38.000Z","msg":"721 新香港"},{"pid":"69c47051fc2ee2ba8aec0b556b0e69d648672a68","tid":1334952,"uid":284309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:15:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c47e144096e93ab94a4ad7d616d53fa275eb31f3","tid":1334952,"uid":284309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:16:12.000Z","msg":"人在外地仲更加清楚自己有幾愛香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833b0fefcbf58d0368756afd8d825605b4186b36","tid":1334952,"uid":284309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"得閒都上黎mon吓post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a712697e8b632babdd95a0762340544369ce51","tid":1334952,"uid":284309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a86aad45f12413f783e4055fe5a7a343564b5e28","tid":1334952,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:21:15.000Z","msg":"對係冇野好講 連外國人都咁關心香港而你就掛住去玩"},{"pid":"243529a3a62e4212ab90afcae09c4ebd7d2caceb","tid":1334952,"uid":284309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:53:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91c9e5a874855a232ab55e7b3d01514655c27d28","tid":1334952,"uid":284309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b638167a08081edea8b3ab7acc86cc37f1885f8","tid":1334952,"uid":35658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:57:13.000Z","msg":"依樣真 近排咁岩去外地做野<br />\nd 人一聽到係香港黎自自然然就會問<br />\n係文宣好機會 佢地聽埋好多中囯人講 好熱切期望知真香港人點睇"},{"pid":"28b2fd02d2066ad3a5aa1ffcf1dbf599dd71de99","tid":1334952,"uid":284309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b638167a08081edea8b3ab7acc86cc37f1885f8","tid":1334952,"uid":35658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"